messageBody:
Hi. I am new here and I wanted to ask for some help.

I use Napster on a regular basis and I want to know what other clients I

should use. What is good? What do you like the best and what is
becomming popular? I want to make sure that I use a client with a lot
of users!

I am somewhat aware of the following: audiogalaxy, scour, opennap, and
napster.

WHAT ELSE SHOULD I BE USING??

--Fred
